./library/prompts/triage/eval-corpus.jsonl:99:{"id":"corpus-66a27d2c7bf3","source_repo":"ddx","expected_class":"atomic","rationale":"closed with commit evidence and no decomposition signal","title":"Remove lossy agent_runner mirror from .ddx/config.yaml and close env-var gap in native config path","description":"Remove DDx's lossy embedded-agent config mirror and close the env-var forwarding gap in the native config path.\n\n## Context\n\nFEAT-006 defines native `.agent/config.yaml` as the authoritative config source for the embedded runner. The current `.ddx/config.yaml` `agent_runner` section is a deprecated mirror that duplicates native runtime config fields. Its precedence semantics are documented in FEAT-006 \"Embedded Runner Configuration Ownership\".\n\n## Goals\n\n- Remove `AgentRunnerConfig` type and `agent_runner` YAML fields from `.ddx/config.yaml` schema once no project uses it\n- Remove `AgentYAMLConfig`, `LLMPresetYAML` mirror types from `cli/internal/agent/runner.go`\n- Remove the `AgentConfigLoader` injection hook and `resolveAgentConfig` fallback path from `agent_runner.go`\n- Apply `AGENT_*` env vars (`AGENT_ROUTE-TARGET`, `AGENT_UPSTREAM-SERVICE`, `AGENT_BASE_URL`, `AGENT_API_KEY`, `AGENT_PRESET`) when resolving from native config, closing the gap documented in `TestConfigPrecedenceEnvVarAppliesInDdxFallbackPath`\n- Wire the `agentRunner()` cmd factory to pass a working-directory path to native config resolution instead of loading the `agent_runner` block\n- Update `TestConfigPrecedenceEnvVarAppliesInDdxFallbackPath` to verify env vars work in the native path after the fix\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- `go build ./...` and `go test ./...` pass with no regressions\n- `.ddx/config.yaml` no longer accepts or uses `agent_runner` fields\n- `AGENT_ROUTE-TARGET` set in the environment overrides the route-target resolved from native `.agent/config.yaml`\n- Existing `.ddx/config.yaml` files with `agent_runner` blocks emit a deprecation warning or are silently ignored (no crash)\n- The migration path in FEAT-006 remains valid","acceptance":"agent_runner mirror removed from DDx config schema; AGENT_* env vars apply in native config path; all tests pass","labels":["ddx","phase:build","kind:implementation","area:agent","area:config","area:cli"],"bead":{"id":"ddx-a3b1c8d2","title":"Remove lossy agent_runner mirror from .ddx/config.yaml and close env-var gap in native config path","status":"closed","issue_type":"task","description":"Remove DDx's lossy embedded-agent config mirror and close the env-var forwarding gap in the native config path.\n\n## Context\n\nFEAT-006 defines native `.agent/config.yaml` as the authoritative config source for the embedded runner. The current `.ddx/config.yaml` `agent_runner` section is a deprecated mirror that duplicates native runtime config fields. Its precedence semantics are documented in FEAT-006 \"Embedded Runner Configuration Ownership\".\n\n## Goals\n\n- Remove `AgentRunnerConfig` type and `agent_runner` YAML fields from `.ddx/config.yaml` schema once no project uses it\n- Remove `AgentYAMLConfig`, `LLMPresetYAML` mirror types from `cli/internal/agent/runner.go`\n- Remove the `AgentConfigLoader` injection hook and `resolveAgentConfig` fallback path from `agent_runner.go`\n- Apply `AGENT_*` env vars (`AGENT_ROUTE-TARGET`, `AGENT_UPSTREAM-SERVICE`, `AGENT_BASE_URL`, `AGENT_API_KEY`, `AGENT_PRESET`) when resolving from native config, closing the gap documented in `TestConfigPrecedenceEnvVarAppliesInDdxFallbackPath`\n- Wire the `agentRunner()` cmd factory to pass a working-directory path to native config resolution instead of loading the `agent_runner` block\n- Update `TestConfigPrecedenceEnvVarAppliesInDdxFallbackPath` to verify env vars work in the native path after the fix\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- `go build ./...` and `go test ./...` pass with no regressions\n- `.ddx/config.yaml` no longer accepts or uses `agent_runner` fields\n- `AGENT_ROUTE-TARGET` set in the environment overrides the route-target resolved from native `.agent/config.yaml`\n- Existing `.ddx/config.yaml` files with `agent_runner` blocks emit a deprecation warning or are silently ignored (no crash)\n- The migration path in FEAT-006 remains valid","acceptance":"agent_runner mirror removed from DDx config schema; AGENT_* env vars apply in native config path; all tests pass","labels":["ddx","phase:build","kind:implementation","area:agent","area:config","area:cli"]}}
